202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4">Silniejsze Relacje z Pacjentami</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Buduje zaufanie i ciągłość opieki między wizytami.</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-teal-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4">Kontrola Lekarza</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Pan/Pani decyduje o oknach odpowiedzi, zapewniając, że komunikacja pozostaje zarządzalna.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-light/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30">Wiadomości Telezdrowotne Asynchroniczne</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Asynchroniczne Wiadomości Telezdrowotne</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Bezpieczny system wiadomości dla pacjentów, w którym pacjenci przesyłają pytania z kontekstem, a lekarze odpowiadają w ustalonych oknach odpowiedzi — ustrukturyzowana opieka, nie czat w czasie rzeczywistym.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Przesyłanie Pytań przez Pacjentów</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Pacjenci wysyłają pytania zdrowotne przez portal lub aplikację, z możliwością załączania raportów lub zdjęć.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">System Odpowiedzi Lekarza</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Lekarze odpowiadają według własnego harmonogramu w określonych ramach czasowych, utrzymując opiekę efektywną i zarządzalną.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Zintegrowany Przepływ Pracy</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Wszystkie pytania i odpowiedzi są przechowywane w dokumentacji zdrowotnej pacjenta, wspierając ciągłość opieki.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-database h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Panel Zarządzania Pytaniami</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Lekarze i zespoły śledzą, priorytetyzują i zarządzają pytaniami pacjentów w jednym zorganizowanym widoku.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Async telehealth messaging interface" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fasynchronous-telehealth-messaging.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fasynchronous-telehealth-messaging.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fasynchronous-telehealth-messaging.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Integrated payment processing for patient messaging" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-payments-for-patient-messaging.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-payments-for-patient-messaging.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-payments-for-patient-messaging.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30">Zintegrowane Płatności</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Zintegrowane Płatności dla Wiadomości Pacjentów</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Przekształć czas lekarza w opłacaną opiekę — każde spotkanie w wiadomościach może być rozliczone, śledzone i opłacone przez Pana/Pani Wirtualną Praktykę.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dollar-sign h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"></line><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Cennik Per-Lekarz</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Ustal różne opłaty za usługi dla każdego lekarza, w oparciu o ich rolę lub specjalizację.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Automatyczne Rozliczenia i Płatności</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Rachunki są generowane automatycznie dla spotkań w wiadomościach. Pacjenci płacą bezpiecznie online, a środki trafiają bezpośrednio na konto Pana/Pani kliniki.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Konfigurowalne Notatki Kontynuacyjne</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Pozwól na zdefiniowaną liczbę odpowiedzi kontynuacyjnych wliczonych w opłatę za jedno spotkanie. Dodatkowe notatki mogą być rozliczane oddzielnie, jeśli potrzeba.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Uczciwa Wartość za Czas Lekarza</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Koniec z nieopłacanymi połączeniami, SMS-ami czy wiadomościami WhatsApp. Czas lekarza jest odpowiednio wynagradzany poprzez ustrukturyzowane, rozliczane wiadomości.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-purple-light/20 text-purple-accent px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-purple-accent/30">Zintegrowany Przepływ Pracy Praktyki</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Zintegrowany Przepływ Pracy Praktyki</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Wiadomości dla Pacjentów nie są izolowanym narzędziem — są częścią Pana/Pani Wirtualnej Praktyki, zapewniając, że każda wiadomość jest bezpieczna, kontekstowa i możliwa do realizacji.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Odpowiedzi Bogate w Kontekst</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Lekarze odpowiadają z pełnym kontekstem z dokumentacji zdrowotnej pacjenta, w tym danymi z monitorów zdrowia i wcześniejszymi konsultacjami.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Stała Dokumentacja</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Pytania i odpowiedzi są zapisywane w dokumentacji pacjenta dla przyszłej referencji i ciągłości opieki.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Przepływy Pracy do Realizacji</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Z każdej wiadomości lekarze mogą zaplanować wizytę, dodać dokument konsultacji, przepisać lub przypisać pacjenta do planu opieki.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Onboarding Nowych Pacjentów</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Osoby szukające drugiej opinii lub pierwszy kontakt są bezproblemowo wprowadzane jako zarejestrowani pacjenci przez portal.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Automatyczne Powiadomienia</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Lekarze są powiadamiani, gdy nadchodzą nowe pytania; pacjenci są powiadamiani, gdy odpowiedzi są gotowe — przez e-mail, SMS lub push aplikacji.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Zintegrowane Rozliczenia</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Każde spotkanie może generować rachunek automatycznie, z płatnościami zbieranymi online i transferowanymi bezpośrednio na konto kliniki.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Integrated practice workflow dashboard" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-practice-workflow.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-practice-workflow.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-practice-workflow.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Secure and compliant communication platform" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fsecure-and-compliant-communication.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fsecure-and-compliant-communication.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fsecure-and-compliant-communication.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-teal-primary/20 text-teal-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-teal-primary/30">Bezpieczna i Zgodna Komunikacja</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Bezpieczna i Zgodna Komunikacja</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Wiadomości dla pacjentów muszą być bezpieczne, prywatne i zgodne. W przeciwieństwie do e-maila, SMS-ów czy aplikacji konsumenckich, które nie są zgodne z RODO, ta funkcja zapewnia, że każda wymiana jest chroniona i odpowiedzialnie przechowywana w Pana/Pani Wirtualnej Praktyce.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Szyfrowanie End-to-End</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Wszystkie wiadomości pacjentów, załączniki i odpowiedzi lekarzy są szyfrowane w przesyłaniu i spoczynku.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Zgodność z RODO</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Zbudowane dla opieki zdrowotnej — komunikacje spełniają najsurowsze standardy bezpieczeństwa i prywatności.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-database h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Zintegrowane z Dokumentacją Zdrowotną</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Rozmowy są automatycznie łączone z elektroniczną dokumentacją zdrowotną pacjenta, a nie rozproszone w niebezpiecznych aplikacjach.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Spokój Ducha dla Lekarzy i Pacjentów</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Pewnie odpowiadaj na pytania, wiedząc, że komunikacja jest bezpieczna, audytowalna i zgodna.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-vibrant/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30 mb-6">PRZYPADKI UŻYCIA</span></div><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-8 mt-4">Typowe Scenariusze Wiadomości dla Pacjentów</h2></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-green-success/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-8 w-8 text-green-success" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Kontynuacja Opieki</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Pytania o leki, kontrole rekonwalescencji, wyjaśnienia wyników</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-blue-vibrant/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-8 w-8 text-blue-vibrant" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Opieka Przewlekła</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Ciągłe wskazówki dla cukrzycy, nadciśnienia, astmy</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-purple-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-8 w-8 text-purple-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Drugie Opinie</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Bezpiecznie przeglądaj raporty i zapewniaj profesjonalne wskazówki nowym pacjentom</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-teal-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Pierwszy Kontakt</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Rozpocznij bezpieczne, udokumentowane relacje prowadzące do pełnych konsultacji</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Allowing doctors to offer telemedicine, remote monitoring health plans, collect payments and the health blog are some of the best features of the Virtual Practice®.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Gerard Saltibus MD</p><p class="text-gray-600">General Practitioner, St. Lucia</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice platform is delivering next-generation medical care. As a multidisciplinary team, we find it powerful and intuitive for organizing patient cases, with clear medical records that support precise documentation and effective care.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Georgios Leon - Metabolic Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is patient messaging in telehealth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patient Messaging is a secure, HIPAA/GDPR-compliant way for patients to send health questions to their provider between visits. Unlike live chat, it's asynchronous — providers respond within defined timeframes, not in real time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why should my clinic use secure patient messaging instead of SMS or WhatsApp?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"SMS and consumer apps aren't secure, compliant, or integrated into your workflow. Secure patient messaging keeps communication encrypted, linked to each patient's health record, and billable — so providers are fairly compensated for their time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers bill for patient messages?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patient Messaging can be configured as a billable service with provider-specific pricing. Bills are auto-generated, patients pay online, and funds are transferred directly to your clinic's account. You can also configure follow-up notes within each encounter."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does patient messaging integrate with the health record?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every question and response is stored in the patient's health record, alongside their health tracker data, labs, and consultations. Providers can schedule appointments, create documents, or assign care plans based on the perspective from a message thread."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is this feature useful for second opinions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patient Messaging is ideal for patients seeking second opinions or initial guidance. New patients submitting questions through your portal are seamlessly onboarded as registered patients in your Virtual Practice."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do notifications work for patient messaging?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Automated notifications are sent at key points: providers receive alerts when a new question arrives, and patients are notified when a response is ready. Notifications can be delivered by email, SMS, or app push."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients attach reports or images to their questions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can include lab results, medical reports, or photos with their messages, giving providers richer context when responding."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does patient messaging help prevent patients from relying only on AI tools?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"When patients don't have easy access to their providers, they often turn to search engines or AI tools for answers. Patient Messaging ensures they can reach their own doctor directly — securely, professionally, and with full context from their health record."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is patient messaging only for established patients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. It's valuable both for existing patients (follow-ups, chronic care, medication questions) and for new patients (initial contact, second opinions). It helps providers grow their patient base while improving continuity of care."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does patient messaging save time for providers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Because it's asynchronous, providers can respond on their schedule within set response windows. This avoids interruptions from phone calls or SMS, reduces no-shows, and ensures that time spent answering patient questions is properly compensated."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What is patient messaging in telehealth?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant tr